sentence: [lip_smack] what first class flights do you have available flying from ontario to tacoma departing before ten in the morning
sq2:
SELECT DISTINCT  '"'||v1.airport_code||'"', '"'||v2.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v2.city_name||'"', '"'||v3.airport_code||'"', '"'||v4.city_code||'"',
 '"'||v4.city_name||'"', v0.departure_time,
 '"'||v5.flight_id||'"', '"'||v6.fare_id||'"', '"'||v7.fare_basis_code||'"',
 '"'||v7.class_type||'"' FROM flight v0,
 airport_service v1, city v2, airport_service v3, city v4, flight_fare v5,
 fare v6, fare_basis v7 
WHERE (((v0.from_airport = ANY v1.airport_code) 
AND ((v1.city_code = ANY v2.city_code) 
AND (v2.city_name = 'ONTARIO'))) AND (((v0.to_airport = ANY v3.airport_code) 
AND ((v3.city_code = ANY v4.city_code) 
AND (v4.city_name = 'TACOMA'))) AND ((v0.departure_time <  1000) 
AND ((v0.flight_id = ANY v5.flight_id) AND ((v5.fare_id = ANY v6.fare_id) 
AND (((v6.fare_basis_code = ANY v7.fare_basis_code) 
AND (v7.class_type = 'FIRST')) AND ( 1 =  1)))))));
sql: ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' ONTARIO ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' TACOMA ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME < 1000 AND FLIGHT . FLIGHT_ID IN ( SELECT FLIGHT_FARE . FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT_FARE WHERE FLIGHT_FARE . FARE_ID IN ( SELECT FARE . FARE_ID FROM FARE WHERE ( FARE.FARE_BASIS_CODE IN ( SELECT FARE_BASIS.FARE_BASIS_CODE FROM FARE_BASIS WHERE FARE_BASIS.CLASS_TYPE = ' FIRST ' ) AND 1 = 1 ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ;
